            "body": "ASAN\n```\n==8754==ERROR: AddressSanitizer: ABRT on unknown address 0x000186fec5e8 (pc 0x000186fec5e8 bp 0x00016fcf6d90 sp 0x00016fcf6d70 T0)\n    #0 0x000186fec5e8 in __pthread_kill+0x8 (libsystem_kernel.dylib:arm64e+0x95e8)\n    #1 0x000186f2e78c in abort+0x90 (libsystem_c.dylib:arm64e+0x7878c)\n    #2 0x000186f2d9e8 in __assert_rtn+0x118 (libsystem_c.dylib:arm64e+0x779e8)\n    #3 0x000101627a8c in redraw_ruler statusline.c:543\n    #4 0x0001005c17d0 in showmode drawscreen.c:1044\n    #5 0x0001005986a8 in update_screen drawscreen.c:716\n    #6 0x0001010672fc in normal_redraw normal.c:1376\n    #7 0x000101065078 in normal_check normal.c:1475\n    #8 0x000101616f14 in state_enter state.c:38\n    #9 0x000100febcb0 in normal_enter normal.c:524\n    #10 0x000100d0eef4 in main main.c:693\n    #11 0x000186c6bda0 in start+0x1b4c (dyld:arm64e+0x1fda0)\n```\n\nthis seems work\n```diff\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/statusline.c b/src/nvim/statusline.c\nindex 34be77ba50..f898176159 100644\n--- a/src/nvim/statusline.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/statusline.c\n@@ -479,7 +479,7 @@ void redraw_ruler(void)\n   int off = wp->w_status_height ? wp->w_wincol : 0;\n   int width = wp->w_status_height ? wp->w_width : Columns;\n   schar_T fillchar = part_of_status ? fillchar_status(&group, wp) : schar_from_ascii(' ');\n-  int attr = win_hl_attr(wp, (int)group);\n+  int attr = part_of_status ? win_hl_attr(wp, (int)group) : HL_ATTR((int)group);\n\n   // In list mode virtcol needs to be recomputed\n   colnr_T virtcol = wp->w_virtcol;\n```",
